PART I]     THE GAZETTE OF PAKISTAN, EXTRA., APRIL   8,  201 8 661 
 
 
 
 
ISLAMABAD,  THURSDAY , SEPTEMBER   24,  2020  
 
 
PART I  
 
Acts, Ordinances, President’s Orders and Regulations  
 
NATIONAL ASSEMBLY SE CRETARIAT  
 
Islamabad, the 23rd  Septmber , 2020 
 
  No. F.22(24)/201 8-Legis .—The following Act of Majlis -e-Shoora 
(Parliament) received the assent of the President on the 22nd September, 2020 is 
hereby published for general information :— 
 
ACT  NO. XXXVI  OF 2020 
AN 
ACT 
further to amend the Islamabad High Court Act, 2010  
 
 WHEREAS  it is expedient further to amend the Islamabad High C ourt Act, 
2010 (XVII of 2010), for the purpose hereinafter appearing;  
 
 It is hereby enacted as follows: – 
 
1. Short title and commencement. –(1) This Act may be called the 
Islamabad High Court (Amendment) Act, 2020.  
 
(661) 
 
Price: Rs. 5.00 
 
[6067(2020 )/Ex. Gaz.].   
662 THE GAZETTE OF PAKISTAN, EXTRA., SEPTEMBER   24,  2020  [PART I 
 
 (2) It shall come into force at once.  
 
2. Amendment of section 3, Act XVII of 2010. —In the Islamabad 
High Court Act, 2010 (XVII of 2010), in section 3, in sub -section (1), for the 
word ―six‖, the word ―nine‖, shall be substituted.  
 
  
 
 
 
TAHIR HUSSAI N, 
Secretary.
